    • setPage

      protected void setPage​(@NotNull @NotNull UIPage<?> page)

      Sets the UIPage whose UI is controlled by this UIPageController to the specified value.

      Details

      1. This method is called internally by the UIPage constructor.
      2. This method should never be called directly, or anywhere outside of the UIPage constructor.
      3. Once the UIPage has been set, onPageBindingComplete() is called to wrap up the operation.
      Parameters:
      page - The UIPage this UIPageController is to control.
